<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id787cc43d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s698u–1"><num value="698u–1">§ 698u–1.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In sections 698u to 698u–7 of this title:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id787cc43e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s698u–1/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Advisory Committee</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Advisory Committee” means the Advisory Committee established under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s698u–5">section 698u–5 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id787cc43f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s698u–1/2"><num value="2" class="bold">(2)</num><heading class="bold"> Preserve</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Preserve” means the Tallgrass Prairie National Preserve established by <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s698u–2">section 698u–2 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id787cc440-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s698u–1/3"><num value="3" class="bold">(3)</num><heading class="bold"> Secretary</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of the Interior.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id787cc441-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s698u–1/4"><num value="4" class="bold">(4)</num><heading class="bold"> Trust</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Trust” means the National Park Trust, Inc., a District of Columbia nonprofit corporation, or any successor-in-interest.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id787cc442-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/333/dI/tX/s1003">Pub. L. 104–333, div. I, title X, § 1003</ref>, <date date="1996-11-12">Nov. 12, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/4205">110 Stat. 4205</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
